        <img src="https://voguebike.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/VOGUE-ARTEMIS-MATT-BLACK.jpg" alt="Damesfietsen" style="width:100%; height:110px; object-fit:cover;">
        <span style="display:block; padding:0.6rem; font-weight:700; font-size:0.82rem; color:#111; text-align:center;">Damesfietsen</span>
